title: Grateful Dead Live at Capital Centre on 1990-03-15
description: Set 1 Jack Straw, Sugaree, Easy To Love You, Walkin' Blues, Althea, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Tennessee Jed, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In Set 2 China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah, Terrapin Station-> Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> I Will Take You Home-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Revolution This date is featured on Terrapin Limited. This show occurred on Phil Lesh's 50th birthday. The last Easy to Love You was performed on 9/3/80, and the last Revolution was performed on 11/8/85.
